DSA-2018-147: Dell EMC Isilon OneFS and Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge Remote Kernel Crash Vulnerability

Dell EMC Identifier: DSA-2018-147
CVE Identifier:  CVE-2018-11071
Severity: High
Severity Rating: CVSS v3 Base Score: 7.5 (AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H)

Affected products:
*             Dell EMC Isilon OneFS versions 7.1.1.x
*             Dell EMC Isilon OneFS versions 7.2.1.x
*             Dell EMC Isilon OneFS versions 8.0.0.x
*             Dell EMC Isilon OneFS versions 8.0.1.x
*             Dell EMC Isilon OneFS versions 8.1.0.x
*             Dell EMC Isilon OneFS versions 8.1.x  prior to 8.1.2

*             Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge versions 8.0.0.x
*             Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge versions 8.0.1.x
*             Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge versions 8.1.0.x
*             Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge versions 8.1.x prior to 8.1.2

Summary:
Dell EMC Isilon OneFS and Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge require a security update to address Remote Kernel Crash vulnerabilities.

Details:

Dell EMC Isilon OneFS versions 7.1.1.x, 7.2.1.x, 8.0.0.x, 8.0.1.x, 8.1.0.x and 8.1.x prior to 8.1.2 and Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge versions 8.0.0.x, 8.0.1.x, 8.1.0.x and 8.1.x prior to 8.1.2 contain a Remote Kernel Crash vulnerability in the isi_drive_d process. An unauthenticated attacker may potentially exploit this vulnerability to crash the server operating system by sending specially crafted input data to the affected system.


Resolution:
The following Dell EMC Isilon OneFS and Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge releases contain a resolution to this vulnerability:
*             Dell EMC Isilon OneFS versions 8.1.2 and later
*             Dell EMC IsilonSD Edge versions 8.1.2 and later


Dell EMC recommends all customers upgrade at the earliest opportunity. Contact Dell EMC Isilon OneFS and Dell EMC Isilon SD Edge customer support to download and install the required rpm file.

Link to remedies:

Registered Dell EMC Online Support customers can download OneFS installation files from the Downloads for Isilon OneFS page of the Dell EMC Online Support site at https://support.emc.com/downloads/15209_Isilon-OneFS.

Registered Dell EMC Online Support customers can download IsilonSD Edge installation files from the 'Downloads for IsilonSD Edge' page on the Dell EMC Online Support site at https://support.emc.com/downloads/39972_IsilonSD-Edge.

Severity Rating
For an explanation of Severity Ratings, refer to Dell EMC Knowledgebase article 468307 (https://support.emc.com/kb/468307). Dell EMC recommends all customers take into account both the base score and any relevant temporal and environmental scores which may impact the potential severity associated with a particular security vulnerability.
